<p>Adrianna Tan is a published writer who has written widely on topics as diverse as: climate change, cultural traditions and festivals, travel tips and advice, the experience of queerness, growing up in Singapore, being Asian American, the immigrant experience, the role of a civic technologist in an age of misinformation and labor exploitation, and many more.</p> 

